      "prompt": "Extract structured data from customer service emails and format it as a strict JSON object. Follow the exact keys and data types shown in the examples.\n\nExample 1:\nEmail: \"Hello, my name is Robert Chen. I'm writing about order #445-B. The package arrived, but it is missing the power cable.\"\nOutput:\n{\n  \"customer_name\": \"Robert Chen\",\n  \"order_id\": \"#445-B\",\n  \"issue_category\": \"Missing Item\",\n  \"issue_description\": \"The package arrived, but it is missing the power cable.\"\n}\n\nExample 2:\nEmail: \"This is Amanda Silva. Order 88192 just got here and it's the wrong color. I ordered blue, not red.\"\nOutput:\n{\n  \"customer_name\": \"Amanda Silva\",\n  \"order_id\": \"88192\",\n  \"issue_category\": \"Wrong Item\",\n  \"issue_description\": \"It's the wrong color. I ordered blue, not red.\"\n}\n\nTarget:\nEmail: \"Hi, I'm Sarah Jenkins. I received order #99281-A yesterday, but the screen on the tablet is completely shattered.\"\nOutput:",
